{"tid":2405790,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"無厘頭0212：開心果","createTime":"2021-02-12T16:01:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T16:01:36.000Z","uid":392287,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"782a159c679b0ecf10970056158e7dea5b4f2a87","tid":2405790,"uid":392287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T16:01:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9wmvyLc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9wmvyLc.png&h=26d071a1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n『不開心就不開心，也別勉強的慰問』<br />\n大年初一，滿街喜氣。一天過去，深夜的你，終於可以放底所有事情，聽一首歌，令自己重回不開心的感覺。因為你知道，開心未必好，不開心亦未必壞，而你就是喜歡這種奇妙的平衡。"}]}